  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Risk of paralyzing medical sector next week - State Medical Officers Association warns",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "If the issue of transport of health workers, including doctors, is not resolved, there is a risk of paralyzing the entire health service from next week.",
        "The Government Medical Officers Association has demanded that the government should find an immediate solution to this problem.",
        "In this regard, Dr. Darshana Sirisena, President of Government Medical Officers Association, said,",
        "Due to the economic crisis in the country, there has been a huge problem in getting fuel for health workers including doctors.",
        "Due to this, we request the government to provide transport facilities for the health workers and implement a proper program.",
        "It seems that the current government is unable to solve the problems in the country. It is crucial at this juncture to come together on a common agenda that everyone can agree on.",
        "In this situation, considering the state of economic crisis of the country, all political parties should think about the country and work together for a common program, he said."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "next week",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
